The paper deals with multi-label classification, which is a common problem in machine learning. The focus of the paper is on addressing the label imbalance problem in multi-label classification with many labels. This problem is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
